@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@wsUrl = ws://localhost:8081
@contentType = application/json

### 获取所有用户（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&page_size=10
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 获取单个用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/get?id=1
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 创建用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "age": 30
}

### 更新用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users?id=1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Updated User",
    "email": "updated@example.com",
    "age": 35
}

### 删除用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users?id=1
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 获取不存在的用户（测试错误处理）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/get?id=9999
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 创建重复邮箱用户（测试错误处理）
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Duplicate Email",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "age": 25
}

### 获取 WebSocket 连接客户端数量（REST API）
GET {{baseUrl}}/ws/clients
Accept: {{contentType}}

### WebSocket 连接（使用 wscat 测试）
// 命令行测试: wscat -c ws://localhost:8081/ws

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: {{contentType}}
